Welcome to ToLiP’s documentation!

TOols Library in Python is a collection of scripts that I’ve written to aid my structural analysis work. This documentation was created to help me stay organized and share my work easily. I will be updating this documentation as I update the existing codes or add additional scripts. My goal is to create scripts that help automate common tasks and calculations.
